{"tid":2135481,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"沈月神隱三個月後終於更新IG　搣甩Baby Fat重拾靚樣","createTime":"2020-08-01T12:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T06:33:16.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"72c26bb31013f0cc10f5c66935c4b0c53febd62f","tid":2135481,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:40:34.000Z","msg":"邱淑貞的大女沈月遺傳了媽咪的優良基因，無論是樣貌還是身材都似足媽咪，更被譽為「最美星二代」。不過今年4月沈月在IG Post相時，就因為臉型圓潤了不少而被指發福，更有網民指她變成了肥版岑麗香，自此她不但關閉了留言功能，還有很長一段時間沒有更新IG，相信不少網民都十分關心她的近況。<br />\n<br />\n日前沈月在IG分享了兩張自拍照，心情大靚的她更大擺V字手勢，相中的她已經告別Baby Fat，變回瓜子臉之餘，五官亦立體了不少，加上皮膚白滑，美貌及氣質都絕對比得上媽咪！雖然沈月在本月中曾為爸爸沈嘉偉的時裝公司旗下品牌做Model拍攝宣傳照，但今次是她相隔3個月後再更新個人IG，狀態Fit爆！"},{"pid":"e3e983c8a4f73f8e310585448c2a13d694981e12","tid":2135481,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":31,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200731/365967034099568640.jpeg/MBoLXuhyzIPNsRTnBUOqQK5W-APWI-X9ZehDRWXoQ0U?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200731%2F365967034099568640.jpeg%2FMBoLXuhyzIPNsRTnBUOqQK5W-APWI-X9ZehDRWXoQ0U%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=adbe76b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb0b0c97ba0d0bbf897ffc9202dbafd539cac2a7","tid":2135481,"uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":94,"score":-83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200623/352070278140006401.jpeg/v2ueV_GFUPvx4yiWL8ET2jq8QZYHxID6Mmy5szJsubM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200623%2F352070278140006401.jpeg%2Fv2ueV_GFUPvx4yiWL8ET2jq8QZYHxID6Mmy5szJsubM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9d0b3e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200731/365967179520282624.jpeg/xJKmL4XeCWeUKne-V_kv44VkpiB4sxn4ToqLtU6Ki7U?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%